      "content": "thanks. i'll try the water. i'm just a bit worried because it was really scary for a second, like i've never felt anything like that before. it was just so fast. you're sure it's just the caffeine? i don't need to like, go to the clinic or anything just in case? i really don't want to deal with the wait times if i can help it.",
